      <div class="col-lg mb-3">
        <h3>以認養代替購買</h3>
        <p>
          動物會知道你對牠的好，只要你願意做出對牠更好的選擇。
        </p>
        <p>實驗動物可以認養嗎？
          依據動保法第 16 條規定：

          進行動物科學應用之機構，應設置實驗動物照護及使用委員會或小組，以督導該機構進行實驗動物之科學應用。</p>
        <p>
          資訊：<span class="badge bg-danger me-2">實驗動物認養</span><span class="badge bg-warning me-2"></span>
        </p>

        <!----<h1>Bunny幫你</h1>---->
        <p></p>
        <h1> <span class="badge bg-secondary">實驗動物領養人登記申請</span></h1>
        <form action="/detailadd" method="post">

          <!---<p>time:</p>
  <p><input type="date" name="a_filltime" required></p>---->

          <p>真實姓名:</p>
          <p><input type="text" name="a_realname" required value=<%=item.a_realname %> ></p>

          <p>信箱:</p>
          <p><input type="text" name="m_email" readonly value=<%=item.m_email %> ></p>

          <p>職業:</p>
          <p><input type="text" name="a_job" required value=<%=item.a_job %> ></p>

          <p>電話:</p>
          <p><input type="text" name="a_phone" oninput="value=value.replace(/[^\d]/g,'')" required value=<%=item.a_phone%> ></p>

          <p>地址:</p>
          <p><input type="text" name="a_address" required value=<%=item.a_address %> ></p>

          <p>備註事項: <a href="donate" target="_blank">查看動物清單</a></p>
          <p><textarea rows="5" cols="20" type="text" name="a_remark"><%= item.a_remark %></textarea></p>

          <div id="exp" hidden><%=item.a_experience %></div><p>有無動物飼養經驗?
          <select class="pets" name="a_experience"></select>
          <script>
            var choose = [{
              name: "無",
              value: "false"
            },
            {
              name: "有",
              value: "true"
            }];

            var exp = document.getElementById('exp');
            console.log(exp.innerHTML);
            var str = '';
            var i;
            for (i = 0; i < choose.length; i++) {
              if (choose[i].value == exp.innerHTML) {
                var option = document.createElement('option');
                option.textContent = choose[i].name;
                option.value = choose[i].value;
                option.selected = 'selected';
                document.querySelector('.pets').appendChild(option);
              }else{
                var option = document.createElement('option');
                option.textContent = choose[i].name;
                option.value = choose[i].value;
                document.querySelector('.pets').appendChild(option);
              }

            }
            option.appendChild(str)
          </script>

          <div id="mtime" hidden><%=item.a_time %></div><p>可面訪時間?
            <select class="meet" name="a_time"></select>
            <script>
              var choose = [{
                name: "平日",
                value: "平日"
              },
              {
                name: "假日",
                value: "假日"
              }, {
                name: "平日與假日皆可",
                value: "平日與假日皆可"
              }];
  
              var mtime = document.getElementById('mtime');
              console.log(mtime.innerHTML);
              var str = '';
              var i;
              for (i = 0; i < choose.length; i++) {
                if (choose[i].value == mtime.innerHTML) {
                  var option = document.createElement('option');
                  option.textContent = choose[i].name;
                  option.value = choose[i].value;
                  option.selected = 'selected';
                  document.querySelector('.meet').appendChild(option);
                }else{
                  var option = document.createElement('option');
                  option.textContent = choose[i].name;
                  option.value = choose[i].value;
                  document.querySelector('.meet').appendChild(option);
                }
  
              }
              option.appendChild(str)
            </script>

          <p><input type="submit" value="送出登記資料"></p>

        </form>

        <!--   <form class="row align-items-end">
